│ Actually, let me think about this more carefully. The function `planContainsAdditionalSimplifications` currently checks if instructions are missing from the VPlan. But scalarized instructions ARE in the     │
│ VPlan (as `VPReplicateRecipe`). So the current logic won't detect them as simplifications.                                                                                                                     │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ The fix is to also check if instructions are being scalarized. We can do this by checking for `VPReplicateRecipe` instances. But we need to be careful: uniform `VPReplicateRecipe` instances are not really   │
│ simplifications - they're just replicating the same value. Non-uniform `VPReplicateRecipe` instances are simplifications because they're creating multiple copies of an instruction that the legacy cost model │
│ might think should be vectorized.                                                                                                                                                                              │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ So the fix should be: return true if there are any non-uniform `VPReplicateRecipe` instances in the VPlan.                                                                                                     │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ Let me create a proper patch that implements this fix.                                                                                                                                                         │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                        │
│ cd /llvm-autofix-deps/llvm/llvm && cat > /tmp/final_patch.txt << 'EOF'                                                                                                                                         │
│ --- a/llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/LoopVectorize.cpp                                                                                                                                                          │
│ +++ b/llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/LoopVectorize.cpp                                                                                                                                                          │
│ @@ -7282,6 +7282,18 @@ planContainsAdditionalSimplifications(VPlan &Plan, ElementCount VF,                                                                                                                     │
│          SeenInstrs.insert(UI);                                                                                                                                                                                │
│      }                                                                                                                                                                                                         │
│    }                                                                                                                                                                                                           │
│ +                                                                                                                                                                                                              │
│ +  // Check if the VPlan contains any non-uniform VPReplicateRecipe, which                                                                                                                                     │
│ +  // indicates scalarization of instructions. This is a simplification that the                                                                                                                               │
│ +  // legacy cost model may not account for.                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ +  Iter = vp_depth_first_deep(Plan.getEntry());                                                                                                                                                                │
│ +  for (VPBasicBlock *VPBB : VPBlockUtils::blocksOnly<VPBasicBlock>(Iter)) {                                                                                                                                   │
│ +    for (VPRecipeBase &R : *VPBB) {                                                                                                                                                                           │
│ +      if (auto *Replicate = dyn_cast<VPReplicateRecipe>(&R))                                                                                                                                                  │
│ +        if (!Replicate->isUniform())                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ +          return true;                                                                                                                                                                                        │
│ +    }                                                                                                                                                                                                         │
│ +  }                                                                                                                                                                                                           │
