│ agree on the best vectorization factor, unless the VPlan contains additional simplifications.                                                                                                                  │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ ROOT CAUSE: The function `planContainsAdditionalSimplifications` was not detecting scalarized instructions as simplifications. Scalarized instructions are represented by non-uniform `VPReplicateRecipe`      │
